      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"TreasureDeepWorkflow-DeepData\">Deep Data</h3><p>This project was also an opportunity to learn about deep rendering, as it was one aspect that I never touched upon in my previous projects … and it turned out to be a lot of fun to deal with.</p><p>To make this work in RfK, all we need to do is change the file type to deep and RenderMan for Katana will output a deep EXR format automatically.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=411\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391698/DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"918\" data-width=\"1696\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621149\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391698\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"419bb442-0f59-496e-a985-1de59d46eae4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=822 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/DEEP_renderOUT_v01.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789138&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=411 1x\"></span><p>This deep data in Nuke allows us to get pixel perfect compositing of very fine detail. It’s also pretty fun to navigate in Nuke too</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"deep3DSpace.gif\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deep3DSpace.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=467\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391698/deep3DSpace.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1036\" data-width=\"1683\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621156\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"deep3DSpace.gif\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/gif\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391698\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f88a2f16-1bc6-484d-a111-62755d09c528\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deep3DSpace.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=934 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deep3DSpace.gif?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789191&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=467 1x\"></span><p>Although it was a new concept for me to deal with Deep compositing, I found it quite a fascinating concept and toolset to use and it was especially excellent to add 2D volumetrics to mimic distance fog during compositing.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"deepUsageA.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deepUsageA.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789233&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391698/deepUsageA.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789233&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"937\" data-width=\"1665\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621162\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"deepUsageA.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391698\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a0c9a436-cd3d-45d4-a358-8bc86fb907e5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deepUsageA.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789233&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/deepUsageA.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789233&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>And finally, Here is a look at my comp treatment and final scene graph in NukeX. You'll need to render the frames locally, but the entire project will hopefully be an insightful look at a productive pipeline, which you can gather ideas from and copy to your personal projects.</p><p>If you're interested in learning more about this great project, make sure to visit Fady's website by following the link on his bio below. </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Nuke_script.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/Nuke_script.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=887\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/657391698/Nuke_script.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1308\" data-width=\"1120\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657621168\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Nuke_script.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"657391698\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"23577b23-7042-4d30-ba53-c10a75227dae\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/Nuke_script.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1120&amp;height=1308 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/657391698/Nuke_script.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762590789264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=887 1x\"></span><p /><hr/>"
